Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.54,0:00:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这个表情 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.60,0:00:11.60,Warning,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\be3\blur3}翻译：梅子 NG 熊猫 校对：小白 影子 后期：风大 时间：果冻 压制 风 A4
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.88,0:00:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她果然不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.12,0:00:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是我们事务所的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们没有男孩子吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.77,0:00:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以和惠惠拍双人照的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这要求有点难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会找找看的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.91,0:00:36.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday　言葉がたりなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.91,0:00:36.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨日 言语不足以表达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:46.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すれ違ったとしても やめないで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:46.58,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使词不达意 也不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:53.75,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もっとわかりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:53.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想更了解你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:01:06.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時にひとりになりたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:01:06.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时 想一人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:18.14,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅をしても心は埋まらない そして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:18.14,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使旅行 内心的空虚也无法填补
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.21,0:01:23.03,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大切な人に気づくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.21,0:01:23.03,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我意识到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.11,0:01:27.21,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつもいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.11,0:01:27.21,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每时每刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.32,0:01:34.23,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう　うまくいくとは限らない毎日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.32,0:01:34.23,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些有点小挫折的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:37.28,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だけど笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:37.28,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你微笑面对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:40.76,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君がくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:40.76,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:48.33,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,たったひとことがどれほど嬉しかったか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:48.33,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多么令我开心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:53.70,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ずっとずっと覚えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:53.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直至今日我也无法忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:01:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 梅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.51,0:02:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小家伙防备心明明很重的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它其实很粘人的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为害羞而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.89,0:02:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.83,0:02:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.34,0:02:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀 突然咬我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.23,0:02:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太舒服了它就会咬人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.04,0:02:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它 没讨厌我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.73,0:02:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 它很缠你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果讨厌你根本就不会让你摸它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.48,0:02:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:41.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅也会很缠我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突…突然间说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}短信 黑泽凪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是…那个…我妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.60,0:02:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用回条短信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿会回的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:02:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天回去的时候有什么打算么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要顺便去哪里逛逛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.69,0:03:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我有点事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.24,0:03:11.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接连两天都被拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是拒绝…可是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.07,0:03:27.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们遇到什么好事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么好事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和真讨厌 好色哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和你们俩很幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和橘很顺利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把幸福展现出来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.05,0:03:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我和麻美这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 健志好讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌就讨厌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能和麻美在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz346.984\pos(836,108)}黑泽凪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz346.984\pos(746,156)}梅也做得出来的食谱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz346.984\pos(698,172)}材料
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz346.984\pos(874,250)}面粉     120g
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz346.984\pos(856,280)}鸡蛋     1个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz346.984\pos(860,316)}无盐黄油 30g
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz346.984\pos(842,344)}砂糖     30g
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz346.984\pos(672,362)}做法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz346.984\pos(900,448)}1.把面粉筛好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz346.984\pos(960,524)}2.用微波炉把黄油加热至柔软\N(不要让它完全化掉哦)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃 怎么做出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在每个步骤中都投入感情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要怕麻烦 只要认认真真来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然就会很好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:33.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我果然还是不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把梅也做得来的食谱发给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 算了吧 我是做不出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.56,0:04:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们交换邮箱地址吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.21,0:04:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(546,560)\frz344.993}我可不许你做奇怪的东西\N给哥哥吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中西他们真是超甜蜜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜蜜的气氛都满满地溢出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是服了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们幸福 我也很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.90,0:05:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑…黑泽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫大和
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是叫不出大和吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 还不习惯只叫名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对会让你叫出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:52.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做好准备哦 梅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是…把面粉筛好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再和面 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用筛子筛面粉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 太难得了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.71,0:06:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈你回来得好早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我有跟你说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.22,0:06:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是曲奇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给男朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.04,0:06:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 面粉放多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.99,0:06:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨手笨脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的 听说已经去办公室打过招呼了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.19,0:06:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈喽 小桃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:48.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 惠惠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事务所离得也近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么惠惠会在我们学校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊 然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.99,0:06:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好找到不错的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就搬过来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拜拜喽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.56,0:07:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和 大和 你听说了没 出大事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:16.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠惠 是惠惠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静 什么惠惠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠惠就是惠惠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你过来看看就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.62,0:07:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dessert杂志的王牌读者模特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北川惠转到咱们学校啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.95,0:07:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠…惠惠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠惠脸好小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好苗条啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的转学过来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定好去哪班了没有?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个 这是我的手机号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不许抢先
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 虽然很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.57,0:08:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是人家通讯录已经存满了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(626,274)\c&HA39CE1&\3c&HEDEDED&}通讯录已满
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.69,0:08:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(632,592)\4c&HE4E5EC&}记录 500/500
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 下次啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后给惠惠发短信 惠惠会很高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和君~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是刚才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很突然…大和君有女朋友么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就直说了 我也想做大和君的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对大和君一见钟情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像找到了自己的白马王子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能陪在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.21,0:09:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有女朋友了也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我们俩会交往得很顺利的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们是俊男美女嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:33.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 对这种只看外表的女人一点兴趣都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等你好久啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我值日
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 我们回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我说了很没礼貌的话 真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不知道你有这么相爱的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…请你把我当成普通的同班同学看待…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们愿意的话…我想和你们俩成为好朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我并不介意…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.57,0:10:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天也说得太过分了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:11:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦 心里的结终于解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 你们之间发生了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没发生过~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.41,0:11:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道就去问大和君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事啊大和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.89,0:11:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你不在意昨天发生了什么么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那个…发生什么事了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别这么简单就相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 真的是什么事都没发生 算啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.31,0:12:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠惠的校服到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 终于有校服穿了 超开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠惠穿得真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.50,0:12:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回教室了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 D班下节课是生物吧？要换教室的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.51,0:12:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么？生物教室在…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.30,0:12:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:12:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠惠还不清楚教室在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:12:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能陪她一起去么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的么 谢谢你大和君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是惠惠！ 真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓紧时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.44,0:13:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么一会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑泽君和惠惠好配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都好有型嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:22.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和惠惠走在一起的大和 想想是不是觉得很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.37,0:13:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我才刚来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.66,0:13:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在校园里还晕头转向的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家又不太会来跟我搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊 和杂志模特在同一个学校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家肯定都不敢和你搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还差得远呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你想 大和君也能当模特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.53,0:13:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我们事务所好像正在找男模呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.38,0:13:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和君要不要去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:14:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事 大和君肯定马上就会火的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.44,0:14:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我没有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 好浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.11,0:14:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算不是杀人凶器了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就是味道这关了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在每个步骤中都投入感情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得自己投入感情了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连猫都不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫都不吃啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别泄气别泄气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和要当模特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要当模特啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是去打一天的工
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是打工?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北川的事务所的男模不够 正发愁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.57,0:15:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法拒绝啊…况且只去一天而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和君肯定适合当模特~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.97,0:15:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 那是不是会给他化妆拍照啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的哦 要不要来摄影棚参观？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 北川
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:15:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去想去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般没什么机会看的的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠惠的摄影现场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 这会给摄影棚的人添麻烦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:08.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常有人来参观
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 那就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅也会来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅也会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.22,0:16:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢的话那我就不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不喜欢 感觉很难为情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有啊 大和君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们事务所的人说拍摄前想开个小会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.84,0:16:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放学之后有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跟梅一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意我 说不定是很要紧的事 你还是去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.39,0:16:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 梅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 梅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:17:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有每天必须一起回家的规定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.67,0:17:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们社长看到照片之后就很中意大和呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非吵着要见一面 真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就去一趟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.80,0:17:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没有一个人回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近总是和黑泽在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一步都感觉好漫长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…怎么尽想这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的主题是 恋人约会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要加进去点动作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太亮了么？怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不换照明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就让他们拿包吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊 很专业的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠惠他们还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠惠 准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.74,0:18:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 惠惠好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:18:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 超可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好厉害啊 这就是所谓的特别气场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩恩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 有气场么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哦有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.74,0:19:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和也准备好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超难为情的诶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头发造型乱乱的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想象和喜欢的人在一起的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.24,0:19:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对 再高兴点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和很有潜质呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.10,0:20:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哦 我说有就有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和真像个专业模特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.60,0:20:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和惠惠看起来像真的情侣似的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.80,0:20:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,额…这是设定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人再靠近点 牵个手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对对 紧紧握住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人简直绝配啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.40,0:20:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是超出预料了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠惠今天看起来也很在状态
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.91,0:20:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们边上看着的人都感觉心跳加速了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和这么夺目 这里的气氛又这么欢乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焦虑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自卑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.65,0:21:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么尽想这些事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.08,0:21:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉大和会越走越远
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.38,0:21:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:49.56,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(736,478)}「为什么…」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:11.80,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\blur3\be3}慣れきた表情の　冷たい朝が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:11.80,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\blur3\be3}喜欢能看到你熟悉表情的清冷早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:17.57,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}あからさまなった意図みせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:17.57,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\blur3\be3}如此直率地向我表明心意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.38,0:22:24.16,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}予言のような空の色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.38,0:22:24.16,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\blur3\be3}天空的颜色如预言般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.30,0:22:29.71,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}そんなに意地悪しないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.30,0:22:29.71,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\blur3\be3}不要这样的捉弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.94,0:22:35.47,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}笑った薄い唇に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.94,0:22:35.47,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\blur3\be3}你的薄唇边挂着微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:41.26,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}傾く影を追いかけた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:41.26,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\blur3\be3}我追寻着你倾斜的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:47.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}君さえもわからないままに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:47.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\blur3\be3}即使我还对你一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:55.75,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}頼りない　もっと抱きしめて放題
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:55.75,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\blur3\be3}虽然不可靠 但请自由地拥抱我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:22:59.07,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}{\blur3\be3}重ねていくいつもの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:22:59.07,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\blur3\be3}总会有许多的交汇处
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.24,0:23:07.38,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}頼りないぐらい　不器用なslow dance
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.24,0:23:07.38,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\blur3\be3}虽然不可靠 笨拙的slow dance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.54,0:23:12.74,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\blur3\be3}揺れる気持ちを乗るの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.54,0:23:12.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}{\blur3\be3}但还是希望你能跟着摇曳的心一起走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.70,0:23:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和去做模特 我为什么会莫名地不安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.40,0:23:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.97,0:23:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开心点开心点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀吼~好兴奋啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.12,0:23:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更难过了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.08,0:23:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅 难过的时候可以抱抱我喵~
